                <head>180. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>
                    <persName corresp="#p_KHA1">Henry Kissinger</persName> visited Ankara March
                    10–11, 1975, as part of a trip to the Middle East March 8–19. He met with the
                    principal Turkish leaders and discussed Cyprus and the Congressional ban on U.S.
                    military aid to Turkey. See <ref target="#d218">Documents 218</ref>–<ref
                        target="#d220">220</ref> for his reports to President <persName
                        corresp="#p_FGR1">Ford</persName> on his meetings.</p>
            </div>
